  <entry>
    <title>API--MaxPoling1D</title>
    <link href="http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/26/API%E2%80%94%E2%80%94MaxPoling1D%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3/"/>
    <id>http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/26/API%E2%80%94%E2%80%94MaxPoling1D%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3/</id>
    <published>2022-01-26T04:31:23.920Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-01T14:48:48.858Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>官方文档：[<a class="link" href="https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/keras/layers/MaxPool1D]">https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/keras/layers/MaxPool1D]<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><h2 id="API–MaxPoling1D"><a href="#API–MaxPoling1D" class="headerlink" title="API–MaxPoling1D"></a>API–MaxPoling1D</h2><h3 id="API说明"><a href="#API说明" class="headerlink" title="API说明"></a>API说明</h3><p>该函数会创建一层池化层，通过在大小为pool_size的空间窗口上取最大值，对输入进行处理。窗口每次的移动步数为strides。</p><p>使用“valid”padding选项时，结果输出的形状为：output_shape=（input_shape-pool_size+1）/strips<br>使用“SAME”填充选项时得到的输出形状是：output_shape = input_shape / strides</p><h3 id="参数说明"><a href="#参数说明" class="headerlink" title="参数说明"></a>参数说明</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tf.keras.layers.MaxPool1D(</span><br><span class="line">    pool_size=2, strides=None, padding=&#x27;valid&#x27;,</span><br><span class="line">    data_format=&#x27;channels_last&#x27;, **kwargs</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="pool-size-空间窗口大小"><a href="#pool-size-空间窗口大小" class="headerlink" title="pool_size  :空间窗口大小"></a>pool_size  :空间窗口大小</h4><h4 id="strides-窗口移动步长"><a href="#strides-窗口移动步长" class="headerlink" title="strides    :窗口移动步长"></a>strides    :窗口移动步长</h4><h4 id="padding-窗口覆盖模式"><a href="#padding-窗口覆盖模式" class="headerlink" title="padding    :窗口覆盖模式"></a>padding    :窗口覆盖模式</h4><p>当使用“valid”padding时：   不会对矩阵外部填充</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = tf.constant([1., 2., 3., 4., 5.])</span><br><span class="line">x = tf.reshape(x, [1, 5, 1])</span><br><span class="line">max_pool_1d = tf.keras.layers.MaxPooling1D(pool_size=2,</span><br><span class="line">   strides=1, padding=&#x27;valid&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">max_pool_1d(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当使用“SAME”padding时：   对矩阵外部填充0</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = tf.constant([1., 2., 3., 4., 5.])</span><br><span class="line">x = tf.reshape(x, [1, 5, 1])</span><br><span class="line">max_pool_1d = tf.keras.layers.MaxPooling1D(pool_size=2,</span><br><span class="line">   strides=1, padding=&#x27;same&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">max_pool_1d(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="data-format-数据形式"><a href="#data-format-数据形式" class="headerlink" title="data_format  :数据形式"></a>data_format  :数据形式</h4><p>Input shape:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">If data_format=&#x27;channels_last&#x27;: 3D tensor with shape (batch_size, steps, features).</span><br><span class="line">If data_format=&#x27;channels_first&#x27;: 3D tensor with shape (batch_size, features, steps).</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Output shape:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">If data_format=&#x27;channels_last&#x27;: 3D tensor with shape (batch_size, downsampled_steps, features).</span><br><span class="line">If data_format=&#x27;channels_first&#x27;: 3D tensor with shape (batch_size, features, downsampled_steps).</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;官方文档：[&lt;a class=&quot;link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/keras/layers/MaxPool1D]&quot;&gt;https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/py</summary>
      
    
    
    
