  <entry>
    <title>opencv图像变换</title>
    <link href="http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/11/opencv%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%98%E6%8D%A2/"/>
    <id>http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/11/opencv%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%98%E6%8D%A2/</id>
    <published>2022-01-11T02:01:16.955Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-01T14:48:48.951Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="图片处理"><a href="#图片处理" class="headerlink" title="图片处理"></a>图片处理</h2><h3 id="图片处理四个步骤"><a href="#图片处理四个步骤" class="headerlink" title="图片处理四个步骤"></a>图片处理四个步骤</h3><p> 1.load<br> 2.info<br> 3.resize<br> 4.check</p><p>共同代码：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">img=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">imgInfo=img.shape</span><br><span class="line">print(imgInfo)</span><br><span class="line">height=imgInfo[0]</span><br><span class="line">width=imgInfo[1]</span><br><span class="line">mode=imgInfo[2]        #颜色</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片缩放"><a href="#图片缩放" class="headerlink" title="图片缩放"></a>图片缩放</h3><p>将长高等比例缩小</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dstHeight=int(height*0.5)           #等比例缩小</span><br><span class="line">dstWidth=int(width*0.5)</span><br><span class="line">dst=cv2.resize(img,(dstHeight,dstWidth))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片剪切"><a href="#图片剪切" class="headerlink" title="图片剪切"></a>图片剪切</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dst=img[100:200,0:300]            #从多少像素切到多少像素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片移位"><a href="#图片移位" class="headerlink" title="图片移位"></a>图片移位</h3><h4 id="使用warpAffine-函数移位"><a href="#使用warpAffine-函数移位" class="headerlink" title="使用warpAffine()函数移位"></a>使用warpAffine()函数移位</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">matShift=np.float32([[1,0,100],[0,1,200]])         #2*3</span><br><span class="line">dst=cv2.warpAffine(img,matShift,(height,width))      #1-data  2-mat  3-info</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>warpAffine变换矩阵实现图像移位</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void cv::warpAffine     (   InputArray      src,</span><br><span class="line">        OutputArray     dst,</span><br><span class="line">        InputArray      M,</span><br><span class="line">        Size    dsize,</span><br><span class="line">        int     flags = INTER_LINEAR,</span><br><span class="line">        int     borderMode = BORDER_CONSTANT,</span><br><span class="line">        const Scalar &amp;      borderValue = Scalar() </span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参数解释：<br>. src: 输入图像<br>. dst: 输出图像，尺寸由dsize指定，图像类型与原图像一致<br>. M: 2X3的变换矩阵<br>. dsize: 指定图像输出尺寸<br>. flags: 插值算法标识符，有默认值INTER_LINEAR，如果插值算法为WARP_INVERSE_MAP, </p><h4 id="for循环移动像素移位"><a href="#for循环移动像素移位" class="headerlink" title="for循环移动像素移位"></a>for循环移动像素移位</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dst = np.zeros(img.shape,np.uint8)</span><br><span class="line">height = imgInfo[0]</span><br><span class="line">width = imgInfo[1]</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(0,height):</span><br><span class="line">    for j in range(0,width-100):</span><br><span class="line">        dst[i,j+100]=img[i,j]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片镜像"><a href="#图片镜像" class="headerlink" title="图片镜像"></a>图片镜像</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">newImgInfo=(height*2,width,mode)</span><br><span class="line">dst=np.zeros(newImgInfo,np.uint8)         #设置画板</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(0,height):                 #for 循环转置像素</span><br><span class="line">    for j in range(0,width):</span><br><span class="line">        dst[i,j]=img[i,j]</span><br><span class="line">        dst[height*2-i-1,j]=img[i,j]</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(0,width):</span><br><span class="line">    dst[height,i]=(0,0,255)      #BGR</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片缩放-1"><a href="#图片缩放-1" class="headerlink" title="图片缩放"></a>图片缩放</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">img=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(&#x27;src&#x27;,img)</span><br><span class="line">matScale=np.float32([[0.5,0,0],[0,0.5,0]])</span><br><span class="line">dst=cv2.warpAffine(img,matScale,(int(width/2),int(height/2)))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="仿射变换"><a href="#仿射变换" class="headerlink" title="仿射变换"></a>仿射变换</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">matSrc=np.float32([[0,0],[0,height-1],[width-1,0]])</span><br><span class="line">matDst=np.float32([[50,50],[300,height-200],[width-300,100]])</span><br><span class="line">matAffine=cv2.getAffineTransform(matSrc,matDst)</span><br><span class="line">dst=cv2.warpAffine(img,matAffine,(width,height))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="旋转变化"><a href="#旋转变化" class="headerlink" title="旋转变化"></a>旋转变化</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">matRotate = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D((height*0.5,width*0.5),45,1)</span><br><span class="line">dst = cv2.warpAffine(img,matRotate,(height,width))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>getRotationMatrix2D函数调用形式</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Mat getRotationMatrix2D(Point2f center, double angle, double scale)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参数详解：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Point2f center：表示旋转的中心点</span><br><span class="line">double angle：表示旋转的角度</span><br><span class="line">double scale：图像缩放因子</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
