  <entry>
    <title>opencv图像灰度处理</title>
    <link href="http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/02/%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/"/>
    <id>http://www.pangtouyu77.fun/2022/01/02/%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/</id>
    <published>2022-01-02T00:49:14.544Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-30T14:27:21.011Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="灰度处理"><a href="#灰度处理" class="headerlink" title="灰度处理"></a>灰度处理</h3><h4 id="imread-函数"><a href="#imread-函数" class="headerlink" title="imread()函数"></a>imread()函数</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">img0=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,0)</span><br><span class="line">img1=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">print(img0.shape)</span><br><span class="line">print(img1.shape)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="cvtColor-函数"><a href="#cvtColor-函数" class="headerlink" title="cvtColor()函数"></a>cvtColor()函数</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">img=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">dst=cv2.cvtColor(img,cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)  #颜色空间转换    1 data   2BGR gra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="R-G-B-grey-取平均值"><a href="#R-G-B-grey-取平均值" class="headerlink" title="R=G=B=grey 取平均值"></a>R=G=B=grey 取平均值</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">img=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">imgInfo=img.shape</span><br><span class="line">height=imgInfo[0]</span><br><span class="line">width=imgInfo[1]</span><br><span class="line">#RGB  R=G=B=gray--------------取平均值</span><br><span class="line">dst=np.zeros((height,width,3),np.uint8)</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(0,height):</span><br><span class="line">    for j in range(0,width):</span><br><span class="line">        (b,g,r)=img[i,j]</span><br><span class="line">        gray=(int(b)+int(g)+int(r))/3             #uint进行相加时容易溢出，所以先取整数再转换回来</span><br><span class="line">        dst[i,j]=np.uint8(gray)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(&#x27;dst&#x27;,dst)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.waitKey(0)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="神奇的心理学公式"><a href="#神奇的心理学公式" class="headerlink" title="神奇的心理学公式"></a>神奇的心理学公式</h4><p>gray=r<em>0.299+g</em>0.587+b*0.114</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">img=cv2.imread(&#x27;image0.jpg&#x27;,1)</span><br><span class="line">imgInfo=img.shape</span><br><span class="line">height=imgInfo[0]</span><br><span class="line">width=imgInfo[1]</span><br><span class="line">#RGB  R=G=B=gray--------------取平均值</span><br><span class="line">dst=np.zeros((height,width,3),np.uint8)</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(0,height):</span><br><span class="line">    for j in range(0,width):</span><br><span class="line">        (b,g,r)=img[i,j]</span><br><span class="line">        b=int(b)</span><br><span class="line">        g=int(g)</span><br><span class="line">        r=int(r)</span><br><span class="line">        gray=r*0.299+g*0.587+b*0.114            #uint进行相加时容易溢出，所以先取整数再转换回来</span><br><span class="line">        dst[i,j]=np.uint8(gray)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="算法优化"><a href="#算法优化" class="headerlink" title="算法优化"></a>算法优化</h3><p>定点运算&gt;浮点运算&gt;移位运算</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#gray=r*0.299+g*0.587+b*0.114</span><br><span class="line">#gray=(r*1+g*2+b*1)/4      #浮点转换为定点运算</span><br><span class="line">gray=(r+(g&lt;&lt;1)+b)&gt;&gt;2       #定点运算转换为移位运算</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;灰度处理&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#灰度处理&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;灰度处理&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;灰度处理&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;imread-函数&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#imread-函数&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=</summary>
      
    
    
    
